          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-262-310L-line-1" n="1">A bard on whom Phœbus his Spirit bestowed,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-310L-line-2" n="2">Resolv'd to acknowledge the bounty he ow'd;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-310L-line-3" n="3">Found out a new Method at once of confessing,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-310L-line-4" n="4">And making the most of so mighty a blessing;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-310L-line-5" n="5">To the God he'd be grateful, but mortals he'd chouse,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-310L-line-6" n="6">By making his patron preside in his house;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-310L-line-7" n="7">And wisely foresaw this advantage from thence,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-310L-line-8" n="8">That the God must in honour bear most of th'expence;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-310L-line-9" n="9">So the Bard he finds drink, &amp; leaves Phœbus to treat,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-310L-line-10" n="10">with the thoughts he inspires, regardless of meat;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-310L-line-11" n="11">Hence they that come hither, expecting to dine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-310L-line-12" n="12">Are always fobb'd off with sheer wit, &amp; sheer wine.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
